/03\/no-better-time-10-days\/","url_meta":{"origin":20903,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dhul-Hijjah: No better time for good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo good deeds can be done at a time better than these first ten days of Dhul-Hijjah.\u201d It was said, \u201cNot even jihad in the way of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cNot even jihad in the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40370,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/05\/if-inward-good\/","url_meta":{"origin":20903,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Deeds: If the inward is good, the outward is good","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the deeds are only like vessels. If the bottom is clean, the top will be clean. If the bottom is spoiled, the top will be spoiled.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4199 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23146,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/10\/best-deeds-consistent-easy\/","url_meta":{"origin":20903,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Habits: Best good deeds done consistently, even if easy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 10, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: By the One who took the Prophet\u2019s soul, peace and blessings be upon him, he did not die until he prayed most of his prayers sitting down. The most beloved deeds to him were righteous deeds that a servant performs regularly, even if they are easy. Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37396,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/18\/bad-character-spoils-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":20903,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Bad character spoils good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 18, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, bad character spoils deeds just as vinegar spoils honey.\u201d Source: Musnad 'Abd ibn H\u0323umayd 799 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0633\u064f\u0648\u0621\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0642\u0650 \u0644\u064e\u064a\u064f\u0641\u0652\u0633\u0650\u062f\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33178,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/11\/faith-jihad-hajj-best-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":20903,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Deeds: Faith, Jihad, Hajj better than all other deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ma\u2019iz al-Tamimi reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked, \u201cWhich deeds are best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFaith in Allah alone, then jihad, and then a blessed pilgrimage are better than all other deeds like the distance between the rising of the sun and its setting.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13457,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/08\/sadness-tested-depression\/","url_meta":{"origin":20903,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sadness: Sins expiated with depression","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf the sins of a servant are numerous and he does not have good deeds to compensate, Allah will afflict him with sadness as an expiation for him.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 25236 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuami